    • Constructor Detail

      • Bid

        protected Bid(User user,
   Thing thing,
   int centsPerHour)
       throws NullIDException

        Create a new Bid object.

        Each bid has a User, placing the bid, and a Thing, upon which the bid is placed. When the bid is created, both objects are notified, and are changed accordingly.
        This means that the User will properly return this bid with User.getBids().

        Parameters:
        user - The user who place a bid.
        thing - The thing being bid on.
        centsPerHour - The value of the bid, in cents per hour.
        Throws:
        NullIDException
